===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{term|yeerly|lang=enm}}, {{term|yerely|lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{term|gearlic|ġēarlīc|yearly, of the year, annual|lang=ang}}, equivalent to {{suffix|year|ly}}. Cognate with {{etyl|sco|-}} {{term|yerelie||yearly|lang=sco}}, {{etyl|fy|-}} {{term|jierliks||yearly|lang=fy}}, {{etyl|nl|-}} {{term|jaarlijks||yearly|lang=nl}}, {{etyl|de|-}} {{term|jährlich||yearly|lang=de}}, {{etyl|sv|-}} {{term|årlig||yearly|lang=sv}}, {{etyl|is|-}} {{term|árlegur||yearly|lang=is}}.

